  "title": "Digital Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>E-Commerce &amp; Digital Marketing: Lead and optimize e-commerce and digital performance campaigns (SEM, SEO, social media) to enhance traffic, engagement, and ROI, while collaborating with regional sales teams to maintain competitive positioning.</li>\n  <li>Implement A/B testing and conversion funnel enhancements to improve user experience, drive higher purchase intent, and boost online sales performance.</li>\n  <li>Loyalty &amp; Personalization: Develop and manage loyalty programs and personalized engagement initiatives using data and AI-driven targeting to strengthen customer retention and lifetime value.</li>\n  <li>Data Analytics &amp; Insights: Track competitor activities and analyze campaign performance, delivering clear, actionable insights through real-time dashboards that support strategic decision-making.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Diploma/Degree in a relevant Business or Marketing discipline</li>\n  <li>At least 2-3 year of working experience in a Digital Marketing function; ideally with FMCG, Consumer Electronics or Consumer Goods industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p>\n<p>Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367</p>\n<p>bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
